bpmn-beta
accTitle: Parallel Task Processing
accDescr: Work is split in parallel across two service tasks and then joined before completion.

start s1 "Trigger"
and g1 "Split"
task:service t1 "Run Background Job"
task:service t2 "Send Notification"
and g2 "Join"
end e1 "Complete"

s1 --> g1
g1 --> t1
g1 --> t2
t1 --> g2
t2 --> g2
g2 --> e1
